title: Five for Revenge 1966 (Spaghetti / Paella Western) directed by Aldo Florio

sources.title: Five for Revenge 1966 (Spaghetti / Paella Western) directed by Aldo Florio
sources.description:
A group of cowboys seek vengeance for their friend's murder and set out to find the bandits responsible. After bandits kill their friend and harm his wife, they embark on a mission to bring the perpetrators to justice. Their quest leads them to confront the ruthless Gonzales brothers and reclaim their friend's son, while seeking retribution for their fallen compadre.

Director: Aldo Florio
Writers: Alfonso Balcázar, Aldo Florio, Bernard C. Schoenfeld
Stars: Guy Madison, Mónica Randall, Vassili Karis, José Manuel Martín, Giovanni Cianfriglia
Genres: Spaghetti Western, Adventure


This film is available with English audio  & subtitles in many languages.

Original title: I 5 della vendetta (1966) 
AKA: Los cinco de la venganza (Spain) | Five Giants From Texas (USA) | Five for Revenge (USA) | No Drums No Trumpets (UK) | Die unerbittlichen Fünf (Germany) | Les 5 de la vendetta (France) | Fem för Hamnden (Sweden) | Oi pente paranomoi tou Texas (Greece) | 5 Gigantes No Texas (Brazil) | 五匹の用心棒 Go-biki no yôjinbô (Japan)
